I woke up on my DEATHBED Sunday night. Airway was inflamed, fatigue, body aches, etc. 
I immediately took HCQ 400mg, Zinc 50mg, Vit C 1000mg. I felt better within 4 hours and continued that regimen twice a day. Today, I’m 100%. Not sure if it was Covid or Flu, but it worked.
